  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $2800 - $3200 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: North</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Normal Working Hours</strong></li><li><strong>Training provided for those without/lesser experience</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Hands-on experience in maintenance and troubleshooting of electrical and/or PLC based systems</strong></li><li><strong>Responsible for maintaining systems located in northern region</strong></li><li><strong>Identification of potential issues</strong></li><li>Liaise with team members, clients or others for problem resolution</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Nitec in Engineering, preferably Electrical, Electronics or Automation</li><li><strong>Candidate without or with lesser experience are welcome as Training will be provided</strong></li><li><strong>Possess valid Class 3 Driving License</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
